metadata.name: Unconscious Movements #1/100
metadata.description:
Evolution of an artist is key without this we would just be a photocopier!  
True power when the unconscious painting experience becomes a natural flow.  
Automatism is a blessing.

This multi edition also acts as a ticket to a competition for a 1/1 Artwork from myself.  
All owners will be entered into the draw once the this multi edition is sold out.
